eu.advance.logistics.flow.engine.api.core

Class UnlimitedPool<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.advance.logistics.flow.engine.api.core.UnlimitedPool<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the pooled object type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Pool<T>, java.io.Closeable, java.lang.AutoCloseable

    public class UnlimitedPool<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Pool<T>
    A pool manager which may return an unlimited amount of objects.

    The pool doesn't keep track of the returned objects.

    Author:
    akarnokd, 2011.10.06.
